       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. T6CL01.
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  WS-INPUTS.
           05  WS-ELAPSED-DAYS       PIC 9(4) VALUE ZERO.
           05  WS-WEEKEND-DAYS       PIC 9(3) VALUE ZERO.
           05  WS-HOLIDAY-DAYS       PIC 9(3) VALUE ZERO.
       01  WS-RESULTS.
           05  WS-WORKING-DAYS       PIC S9(5) VALUE ZERO.
           05  WS-DELAY-DAYS         PIC S9(5) VALUE ZERO.
           05  WS-PENALTY-AMT        PIC 9(7)V99 VALUE ZERO.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       1000-MAIN.
           ACCEPT WS-ELAPSED-DAYS
           ACCEPT WS-WEEKEND-DAYS
           ACCEPT WS-HOLIDAY-DAYS
           PERFORM 2000-CALCULATE-PENALTY
           DISPLAY WS-PENALTY-AMT
           STOP RUN.
       2000-CALCULATE-PENALTY.
           COMPUTE WS-WORKING-DAYS =
              WS-ELAPSED-DAYS - WS-WEEKEND-DAYS - WS-HOLIDAY-DAYS
           COMPUTE WS-DELAY-DAYS = WS-WORKING-DAYS - 7
           IF WS-DELAY-DAYS > ZERO
              COMPUTE WS-PENALTY-AMT = WS-DELAY-DAYS * 500
           END-IF.
